headline: JPMorgan Raises Lululemon (LULU) Q4 2025 EPS Estimate Following ICR Conference Meeting Citing Updated 2026 Projections
summary: Lululemon Athletica Inc. (NASDAQ:LULU) is one of the stocks that should double by 2030. On January 20, JPMorgan raised the price target on Lululemon to $209 from $203 and maintained a Neutral rating.
